                    <p class="tech-text">Cloud-Based Storage and Accessibility revolutionize the way surveillance footage is stored, accessed, and managed. This feature involves securely storing surveillance data in the cloud, allowing authorized users to access footage from any location with internet connectivity. Cloud-based storage not only provides scalability and flexibility but also ensures data integrity and accessibility, enabling efficient retrieval of critical information when needed.</p>

                </section>

